2.	Run the SQL file (zomato_analysis.sql) 
3.	Execute queries step-by-step to view results 
________________________________________
🔹 Key Takeaways
•	Strong customer retention (though dataset-biased) 
•	Revenue is not concentrated among a few users 
•	Customers order infrequently 
•	Moderate cancellation rate 
•	Reliable delivery performance 
•	Demand varies across cities and days 
________________________________________
🔹 Final Note
This project is based on a sample dataset, so some results may not fully reflect real-world behavior. The focus here is on the analytical approach, query logic, and interpretation of results.
